CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 1, 1955, pg. 21, reads: "Tan Stalwarts Used Sparingly in Steeler Victory, 'Bench Spectators" Watch Teammates Trip Cards, 14 - 7; Dave Mann... can really punt."
TitMainTitle: Chicago Cardinals football players, including no. 33 Dave Mann, standing on Forbes Field during game against the Pittsburgh Steelers, at night
